Package: countcheck
Type: Package
Title: Detecting Count Anomalies Using Bayesian Hierarchical Models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jens Meydam
Maintainer: Jens Meydam <jmeydam@gmail.com>
Description: Dertermines upper control limits for count data.
  Reasonable results also in cases with few or no observed events.
  HTML reports.
    Model and code are based on examples in McElreath [2020] and
  Gelman et al. [2014].
